cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a modification to the Batch Normalization technique for improving performance in visual tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for enhancing instance-specific information, which suggests it could belong to categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves a self-attention mechanism, which could place it in categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
